OL,3,CWarm weather continues as millions of
OL,4,Cdrivers to hit roads over weekend
OL,6,FWarm and sunny weather is set to
OL,7,Fcontinue as drivers have been warned
OL,8,Fto expect the busiest summer getaway
OL,9,Fon the roads in four years.
OL,11,FUK temperatures have topped 30C during
OL,12,Fthe past 11 days and the grip of the
OL,13,Flong, hot summer is set to last for at
OL,14,Fleast seven to 10 more days,
OL,15,Fforecasters said.
OL,17,FAnd the RAC estimated that 14.1
OL,18,Fmillion motorists will embark on
OL,19,Fjourneys for holidays or day trips
OL,20,Fbetween Friday and Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
