FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784249267
OL,3,CWarm weather continues as millions of
OL,4,Cdrivers to hit roads over weekend
OL,6,FFriday and Sunday will each see an
OL,7,Festimated 3.4 million.
OL,9,FA further 6.8 million trips will be
OL,10,Fspread across the three-day period,
OL,11,Fwith drivers unsure which exact day
OL,12,Fthey will hit the road.
OL,14,FMet Office spokesman Graham Madge
OL,15,Fsaid: "The settled and fine conditions
OL,16,Fpeople are currently enjoying look
OL,17,Flocked in for the next seven to 10
OL,18,Fdays and are likely to remain strong."
OL,26,@wD@GOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
