OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784249267
OL,3,CWarm weather continues as millions of
OL,4,Cdrivers to hit roads over weekend
OL,6,FThe Met Office said Wales is sitting
OL,7,F2.2C above an average of around 19.3C,
OL,8,Fand while Scotland and Northern
OL,9,FIreland have remained closer to their
OL,10,Fseasonal norms of 17.3C and 18.6C,
OL,11,Fthey are still running above average
OL,12,Fat 0.9C and 1.3C respectively.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
